text.tspan: In the days of our youth
We treasure the Word of God
As a child, we may read it
When we come to God’s Word,
As we love Him and seek Him,
So that God’s light shines brightly
In the Word of our God,
To be faithful to read it
Yes, we read and we pray,
And we pray what we read—
In the days of our youth,
From a child, know the Scriptures
And let HIm have a way
All your days on the earth.
